data.title: Jesus of Montreal
data.meta_description: Where to watch Jesus of Montreal (1989) starring Lothaire Bluteau, Catherine Wilkening, Johanne-Marie Tremblay and directed by Denys Arcand.
data.text: A small group of actors who are putting on an interpretive Passion Play in Montreal begin to experience a meshing of their characters and their private lives as the production takes form against the growing opposition of the Catholic Church.
